user: I'm interested in learning more about social media campaigns. My friend recently launched a brand that sells clothing and accessories, and I helped her create content for her Instagram and Facebook pages to promote it. I was wondering if you could give me some tips on how to increase engagement on those platforms, especially since her campaign was pretty successful.
